code: // -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- // All mutating methods must fail // -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- @Override public void addAllToProperties(Properties props) {     // override to make the UnmodifiableConfigurationTest happy     super.addAllToProperties(props). }
